UID:1c5cad3e6a4446c6026f6b1724a07a21@mercurytheater.org
DESCRIPTION:Enfrascada by Tanya Saracho April 24-May 10 TICKETS Practical\
 , down-to-earth Alicia has had her heart broken and her world shattered\, 
 but her girls\, Yesinia and Carolina\, know what to do! With Alicia's cous
 in Lulu they launch into a madcap plan of magical manipulation with a litt
 le Santeria\, a dash of Hoodoo\, and a whole heap of Brujeria! Get 'engros
 sed' in this dark Latine comedy about friendship\, magic\, and finding you
 rself after your world falls apart Beulah Vega\, Stage Director .fe-block-
 b043b51c14f6706e3380 {mix-blend-mode: \; }
LOCATION:Mercury Theater\, 3333 Petaluma Blvd N\, Petaluma\, CA 94952
